                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960406-9-off50 t17960406-9-cd51"></join>, fifty-four yards of silk ribbon, value 27s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17960406-9-victim126" type="victimName">
                           Ann 
